---
---
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">How I Help Parents</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Providing practical clarity and guidance when you feel overwhelmed by your child’s developmental or behavioural needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover-lift relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-sky/10 rounded-bl-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-cream text-brand-trust rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-sm relative z-10">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3 relative z-10">Understand the concern</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          Navigate concerns around ADHD, autism, challenging behaviour, emotional regulation, and school difficulties with a professional sounding board.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover-lift relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-bl-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-cream text-brand-trust rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-sm relative z-10">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3 relative z-10">Get practical next steps</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          Move from confusion to action with tailored parent guidance, functional home routines, tested strategies, and a clear support plan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover-lift relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-lavender/10 rounded-bl-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-cream text-brand-trust rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-sm relative z-10">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3 relative z-10">Feel less confused</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          Gain clear, jargon-free explanations of psychological reports, formal assessments, and exactly what your child needs to thrive.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
